OL,7,FThere are serious concerns about South
OL,8,FWales Fire and Rescue Service's
OL,9,F"performance in keeping people safe"
OL,10,Fand its ability to "mitigate risks for
OL,11,Fthe public", a new inspection report
OL,12,Fhas found.
