OL,3,CConcerns raised over South Wales
OL,4,CFire's 'performance in keeping people
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FAn inspection by His Majesty's
OL,8,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Services (HMICFR), which
OL,10,Ftook place between July and November
OL,11,F2024, found the service's record-
OL,12,Fkeeping process means it cannot
OL,13,Feffectively "help protect
OL,14,Ffirefighters, the public and property
OL,15,Fduring emergencies".
OL,17,F"The service doesn't always prioritise
OL,18,Fthose most at risk", the report said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
