OL,3,CConcerns raised over South Wales
OL,4,CFire's 'performance in keeping people
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FThe service said it already has "a
OL,8,Frobust plan for dealing with these
OL,9,Frecommendations", adding that major
OL,10,Fchanges had been made to the service
OL,11,Fsince the inspection took place.
OL,13,FHMICFR usually only assesses fire
OL,14,Fservices in England, but following a
OL,15,Fseries of scandals at South Wales Fire
OL,16,Fand Rescue Service, the four Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment-appointed commissioners
OL,18,Foverseeing the service requested the
OL,19,Finspection to "get a benchmark for
OL,20,Ffuture improvement".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
