OL,3,CConcerns raised over South Wales
OL,4,CFire's 'performance in keeping people
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FIn January 2024, a separate report was
OL,8,Fpublished by Fenella Morris KC after
OL,9,FITV reported allegations of sexual
OL,10,Fassault at the service. That report
OL,11,Fincluded details of misogyny, racism
OL,12,Fand homophobia and led to the chief
OL,13,Ffire officer Huw Jakeway resigning.
OL,15,FAn interim fire chief was appointed,
OL,16,Fbut soon after taking up the role, ITV
OL,17,Flearned he was the subject of an
OL,18,Femployment tribunal, accused of
OL,19,Fbullying. Stuart Millington denied the
OL,20,Fallegation and has faced no further
OL,21,Faction.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
