OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FIn November, Mr Millington was
OL,8,Freplaced by the current chief fire
OL,9,Fofficer, Finn Monahan. Mr Monahan said
OL,10,Fhe would "completely change the
OL,11,Fculture".
OL,13,FThis latest inspection took place
OL,14,Fbetween July and November 2024, with
OL,15,Finspectors assessing a variety of
OL,16,Faspects in the service, including fire
OL,17,Fprevention and protection, community
OL,18,Ffire safety and culture and values.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
