OL,7,FThe HMICFR report author said: "Sadly,
OL,8,FI have concerns about the service's
OL,9,Fperformance in keeping people safe and
OL,10,Fsecure from fire and other risks.
OL,12,F"In particular, I have concerns about
OL,13,Fthe effectiveness of its strategies
OL,14,Ffor making sure its activities
OL,15,Fconsistently identify, prioritise and
OL,16,Fmitigate risks for the public.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
