OL,3,CConcerns raised over South Wales
OL,4,CFire's 'performance in keeping people
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,F"I am also concerned that it doesn't
OL,8,Fhave effective systems and processes
OL,9,Fin place to gather and record relevant
OL,10,Fand uptodate risk information to
OL,11,Fhelp protect firefighters, the public
OL,12,Fand property during emergencies."
OL,14,FCommunity fire safety was found to be
OL,15,F"inconsistently effective at
OL,16,Fidentifying local risks and
OL,17,Fpriorities".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
