OL,3,CConcerns raised over South Wales
OL,4,CFire's 'performance in keeping people
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,F"The service needs to be more
OL,8,Feffective in tackling bullying,
OL,9,Fharassment and discrimination. In our
OL,10,Fstaff survey, 17 per cent of
OL,11,Frespondents told us they had felt
OL,12,Fbullied or harassed at work in the
OL,13,Fpast 12 months."
OL,15,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,16,Ftold ITV News that work had been
OL,17,Fundertaken since the inspection to
OL,18,Faddress the issues raised.
