OL,7,FIn a statement, Fin Monahan said: "The
OL,8,Freport is a hard read. The main areas
OL,9,Ffor us to improve in the report are
OL,10,Funderstanding the risk of fire and
OL,11,Fother emergencies and protecting the
OL,12,Fpublic through fire regulations.
OL,14,F"I welcome this report, this is the
OL,15,Ffirst time we have been exposed to
OL,16,Fthis deep inspection regime. Let's
OL,17,Fremember a lot of time has elapsed
OL,18,Fsince the inspection.
