OL,7,F"It began before my arrival and
OL,8,Fconcluded during my second week in the
OL,9,Fservice; it is a snapshot in time from
OL,10,Fsix months ago. Much has changed since
OL,11,Fthen."
OL,13,FThe service added: "We're listening,
OL,14,Flearning, and seeking to lead the way
OL,15,Fin fire and rescue service
OL,16,Ftransformation of cultures, and we are
OL,17,Fcommitted to delivering exceptional
OL,18,Fservice."
