OL,7,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue's
OL,8,Fcommissioners said: "This report
OL,9,Fprovides a solid assessment of
OL,10,Fperformance against a comprehensive
OL,11,Frange of factors that are commonly
OL,12,Fassessed against in the rest of the UK
OL,13,Ffire and rescue services.
OL,15,F"We are pleased that, since the
OL,16,Finspection in late 2024 that a
OL,17,Fconsiderable amount of progress has
OL,18,Fbeen made in addressing the
OL,19,Frecommendations in the report."
