OL,7,FAccording to HMICFR guidelines, South
OL,8,FWales Fire and Rescue Service now has
OL,9,F28 days to "develop an action plan" to
OL,10,Faddress the issues identified within
OL,11,Fthe report.
OL,13,FA Welsh Government statement said: "We
OL,14,Fappointed commissioners to South Wales
OL,15,FFire and Rescue Service in 2024
OL,16,Fbecause we had serious concerns about
OL,17,Fthe service's ability to function
OL,18,Fsafely and effectively.
