OL,7,F"The commissioners, and the new chief
OL,8,Ffire officer of South Wales Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service, have already begun
OL,10,Fbuilding the HMICFRS recommendations
OL,11,Finto their transformation programme
OL,12,Fand supporting delivery plan.
OL,14,F"We will continue to work with the
OL,15,Fcommissioners and the chief fire
OL,16,Fofficer on the delivery of their
OL,17,Fimprovement priorities."
